# Technology Stack Details

## UI Component Libraries

### Radix UI Primitives
The project uses extensive Radix UI components for accessible, unstyled primitives:
- **Alert Dialog** - Modal dialogs for confirmations
- **Avatar** - User profile images
- **Checkbox** - Form checkboxes
- **Collapsible** - Expandable content sections
- **Dialog** - Modal dialogs
- **Dropdown Menu** - Context menus
- **Icons** - Icon library
- **Label** - Form labels
- **Popover** - Floating content
- **Radio Group** - Radio button groups
- **Scroll Area** - Custom scrollable areas
- **Select** - Dropdown selects
- **Separator** - Visual dividers
- **Slot** - Component composition
- **Switch** - Toggle switches
- **Tabs** - Tabbed interfaces
- **Tooltip** - Hover information

### Additional UI Libraries
- **Input OTP** - One-time password inputs
- **React Day Picker** - Date picker component
- **React Top Loading Bar** - Progress indicators
- **Sonner** - Toast notifications
- **CMDK** - Command palette interface

## Data & State Management

### TanStack Ecosystem
- **TanStack Query** - Server state management with caching
- **TanStack Router** - Type-safe client-side routing
- **TanStack Table** - Headless table component

### State Management
- **Zustand** - Lightweight state management
- **React Hook Form** - Form state management
- **Zod** - Schema validation

## Styling & Animation
- **Tailwind CSS v4** - Utility-first CSS framework
- **Tailwind Merge** - Utility class merging
- **Class Variance Authority** - Component variant management
- **CLSX** - Conditional class names
- **TW Animate CSS** - Tailwind animations

## Development Tools
- **TypeScript** - Type safety
- **ESLint** - Code linting with TypeScript support
- **Prettier** - Code formatting with import sorting
- **Knip** - Unused dependency detection
- **Vite** - Build tool and dev server

## Utilities
- **Axios** - HTTP client
- **Date-fns** - Date manipulation
- **JS Cookie** - Cookie management
- **Faker.js** - Mock data generation (dev dependency)
